body:
Are you sure you're looking at the right builder? The builder columns are
opportunistically populated (on the front page there are as many columns as
there are core builders, on the subrepo page only columns that have results
for that builder are shown), so they're not equivalent on each page.

Can you provide screenshots to illustrate the problem?
